{
  "texts": [
    "Nonetheless, in essay content scoring tasks, the validity of these different segments likely needs to be evaluated separately (Horbach et al., 2022).",
    "For this reason, essays might require segmentation before different sub-topics can be addressed differently.",
    "In natural language processing, segmentation is a widely researched topic with a long history (Choi, 2000).",
    "The most obvious examples of this are tokenisation and sentence splitting.",
    "However, semantic segmentation procedures go beyond these basic preprocessing steps."
  ]
}